cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CL 

The paper deals with the task of determining the probability that a questioned handwritten word has been written by a known writer, which falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also involves feature extraction and comparison, which can be related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
